@startuml
title UML State Machine Diagram for Staff Member Class

[*] --> Assigned

state "Assigned" as Assigned
Assigned : entry / staff member assigned to a client or campaign
Assigned : do / manage tasks and assignments
Assigned : exit / no specific action

state Unassigned
Unassigned : entry / staff member unassigned from all clients/campaigns
Unassigned : do / reset status
Unassigned : exit / staff member is now available for new assignments

state Switching
Switching : entry / staff member switching between different assignments
Switching : do / update current assignment
Switching : exit / new assignment set

state Unemployed
Unemployed : entry / staff member leaves the job
Unemployed : do / mark as unemployed
Unemployed : exit / staff member is no longer active in the system

state Archived
Archived : entry / former employee's record archived
Archived : do / store historical data
Archived : exit / data is now archived and not accessible for new assignments

Assigned --> Switching
Switching --> Assigned
Assigned --> Unassigned
Unassigned --> Assigned
Assigned --> Unemployed
Unemployed --> Archived
Archived --> [*]

@enduml
